      • viewAll

        public static java.util.LinkedList<java.lang.Object> viewAll(java.lang.Object obj,
                                                             java.sql.ResultSet rs)
        Converts data from resultSet to a list of objects. Return the list of objects generated by the data from the resultset sent as parameter. The obj argument will be the type of the objects in the list. The method will return a null pointer if rs is empty.
        Parameters:
        obj - an Object giving the type of the objects in the list
        rs - a ResultSet which contains the data to be converted in a list
        Returns:
        a LinkedList with the object's type, same as the obj parameter
